---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Careers | Join Block Party Productions"
  description="Discover exciting career opportunities at Block Party Productions. We're looking for passionate individuals to join our San Francisco hospitality team."
  ogTitle="Careers at Block Party Productions"
  ogDescription="Explore your future with Block Party Productions. We're on the lookout for dedicated individuals ready to make a difference in the hospitality industry."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section style="position: relative; min-height: 60vh; display: flex; align-items: center; overflow: hidden; background: #111;">
    <img
      src="/images/hero-careers.jpg"
      alt="Join the Block Party Productions team"
      style="position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; opacity: 0.45;"
    />
    <div style="position: relative; z-index: 1; padding: 3rem 1.5rem; max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%;">
      <h1 class="heading_h2" style="color: #fff; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; max-width: 640px;">
        Join our vibrant hospitality team
      </h1>
      
        href="https://jobs.ashbyhq.com/blockparty"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="button on-inverse is-secondary"
      >
        View Open Roles
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
  <section style="max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 6rem 1.5rem;">
    <div id="careers-layout" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 5rem; align-items: start;">

      <!-- Left: text -->
      <div>
        <p class="paragraph_large" style="font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 1.5rem;">
          BlockParty is a cultural design studio and modern restaurant collective reimagining how people gather.
        </p>
        <p class="paragraph_large" style="color: #4b5563; margin: 0 0 1.5rem;">
          We don't just serve meals — we create soulful, intentional spaces that restore belonging, spark curiosity, and design community through experience.
        </p>
        <p class="paragraph_large" style="color: #4b5563; margin: 0 0 1.5rem;">
          From venues like Fireside, Longhouse, BuenaVida Cantina, and Lot F, we host curated experiences that live at the intersection of food, culture, creativity, and connection. We are building a new kind of infrastructure for meaningful human gathering — and we're doing it through artful business.
        </p>
        <p class="paragraph_large" style="color: #4b5563; margin: 0 0 2.5rem;">
          Our venues aren't just locations. They are portals, and your work will be the invitation. We're building a new blueprint for gathering. If that excites you more than it intimidates you, let's talk.
        </p>
        <p class="text-color_secondary" style="margin: 0 0 2.5rem; line-height: 1.7;">
          Explore open roles, learn about our benefits, and see how you can help shape memorable experiences for guests and colleagues alike.
        </p>
        
          href="https://jobs.ashbyhq.com/blockparty"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="button is-secondary"
        >
          Join Us
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: values cards -->
      <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem;">

        <div style="background: #f9fafb; border-radius: 1rem; padding: 2rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
          <h3 class="heading_h4" style="margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">Culture first</h3>
          <p class="paragraph" style="margin: 0; color: #4b5563;">
            We build spaces where people feel they truly belong — and that starts with how we treat our own team.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="background: #f9fafb; border-radius: 1rem; padding: 2rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
          <h3 class="heading_h4" style="margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">Creative work</h3>
          <p class="paragraph" style="margin: 0; color: #4b5563;">
            Every event is a canvas. We invite our team to bring ideas, energy, and craft to everything they do.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="background: #f9fafb; border-radius: 1rem; padding: 2rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
          <h3 class="heading_h4" style="margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">Real impact</h3>
          <p class="paragraph" style="margin: 0; color: #4b5563;">
            You're not just filling a role — you're helping shape the future of how San Francisco gathers and connects.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="background: #000; border-radius: 1rem; padding: 2rem; color: #fff;">
          <h3 class="heading_h4" style="color: #fff; margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">Ready to apply?</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); margin: 0 0 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Browse all open positions on our jobs board.
          </p>
          
            href="https://jobs.ashbyhq.com/blockparty"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="button on-inverse"
            style="display: block; text-align: center;"
          >
            See Open Roles
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    #careers-layout { grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr !important; }
  }
</style>